    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Start Your Journey as a Forklift Operator!</h2>Start with a small warehouse, small forklift and a little planks factory and grow your business to the levels no one has ever seen before.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143880/extras/544c4b613f3cd22ed50cd6e118ee880e.poster.avif?t=1735424474\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143880/extras/544c4b613f3cd22ed50cd6e118ee880e.webm?t=1735424474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143880/extras/544c4b613f3cd22ed50cd6e118ee880e.mp4?t=1735424474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Take Over the World!</h2>Manage your company to success! Purchase every factory and upgrade them to their best, you'll have a warehouse packed full of products in no time!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143880/extras/3667ceee83a6ff30ca2b8f69a4025255.poster.avif?t=1735424474\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143880/extras/3667ceee83a6ff30ca2b8f69a4025255.webm?t=1735424474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143880/extras/3667ceee83a6ff30ca2b8f69a4025255.mp4?t=1735424474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Earn the Success!</h2>Upgrade cargos for your best interest! Maybe you'd want to produce more, maybe you'd want to sell for more... hmm... how about both?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143880/extras/b8182f31c3b1c26dc911d77a29eb46e7.poster.avif?t=1735424474\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143880/extras/b8182f31c3b1c26dc911d77a29eb46e7.webm?t=1735424474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143880/extras/b8182f31c3b1c26dc911d77a29eb46e7.mp4?t=1735424474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Improve Yourself</h2>Level up and invest on your personal skills! If you can not reach to success, it will reach to you...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143880/extras/2955dd09abaf532d73620ca9e9f6d9c6.poster.avif?t=1735424474\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143880/extras/2955dd09abaf532d73620ca9e9f6d9c6.webm?t=1735424474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143880/extras/2955dd09abaf532d73620ca9e9f6d9c6.mp4?t=1735424474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How About Competition?</h2>You'll have a lot of competitors! Will you co-exist with them, letting them earn all the bucks? Or, will you overpower and purchase all of them to own the world?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143880/extras/5953e95d54a0be2ef2e12c2c647244c8.poster.avif?t=1735424474\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143880/extras/5953e95d54a0be2ef2e12c2c647244c8.webm?t=1735424474\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143880/extras/5953e95d54a0be2ef2e12c2c647244c8.mp4?t=1735424474\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>After all, the only thing keeping you from the top is yourself...</strong>",
